Spring Tech Notes:
************************
1. Folder Structure creation (src/target/pom.xml)
	mvn archetype:generate 
	-DgroupId={project-packaging}
	-DartifactId={project-name}
	-DarchetypeArtifactId={maven-template} 
	-DinteractiveMode=false
	
Simple Jar Project	mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.dhanam.streamtest -DartifactId=spring-core-project -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart -DinteractiveMode=false
Simple War Project : mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.mkyong.web -DartifactId=java-web-project -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-webapp -DinteractiveMode=false

2. what configuration needs to be done at pom.xml	
	Dependency Cross Check vs (Original & New)
	
3. Spring-Core (Object creation out of Java, from xml file object injection will happen)
	xml file creation
	
	Spring-MVC
		web.xml
		{servletname}-servlet.xml
		@Controller
		
	
